The discussions I have seen regarding the `keepMounted` prop on `Menu` have been related to accessibility rather than SEO/SSR (though I see now that the prop description on `Modal` mentions SEO). For the accessibility use cases, a slight delay on the rendering of the menu items (rather than being part of the initial rendering) will not cause any issues.

The delay is due to `Portal` (`Menu` uses `Popover` which uses `Modal` which uses `Portal`) [triggering the rendering of its children via an effect](https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui/blob/v4.5.0/packages/material-ui/src/Portal/Portal.js#L26).

The only way I see to work around this is to leverage the [disablePortal prop](https://material-ui.com/api/modal/#props) (in addition to `keepMounted`) on `Menu/Popover/Modal/Portal`.

```
        &lt;Select
          value={state.age}
          onChange={handleChange}
          inputProps={{
            name: &quot;age&quot;,
            id: &quot;age-simple&quot;
          }}
          MenuProps={{ keepMounted: true, disablePortal: true }}
        &gt;
          &lt;MenuItem value=&quot;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;em&gt;None&lt;/em&gt;
          &lt;/MenuItem&gt;
          &lt;MenuItem value={10}&gt;Ten&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
          &lt;MenuItem value={20}&gt;Twenty&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
          &lt;MenuItem value={30}&gt;Thirty&lt;/MenuItem&gt;
        &lt;/Select&gt;
```

[![Edit Select menu items on initial render](https://codesandbox.io/static/img/play-codesandbox.svg)](https://codesandbox.io/s/select-menu-items-on-initial-render-n58lp?fontsize=14)

I don&#39;t use SSR myself and haven&#39;t tested this solution in an SSR environment, but I believe it should do the trick.

Code resources:

* [Select](https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui/blob/v4.5.0/packages/material-ui/src/Select/Select.js#L39)
* [SelectInput](https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui/blob/v4.5.0/packages/material-ui/src/Select/SelectInput.js#L311)
* [Menu](https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui/blob/v4.5.0/packages/material-ui/src/Menu/Menu.js#L132)
* [Popover](https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui/blob/v4.5.0/packages/material-ui/src/Popover/Popover.js#L376)
* [Modal](https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui/blob/v4.5.0/packages/material-ui/src/Modal/Modal.js#L225)
* [Portal](https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui/blob/v4.5.0/packages/material-ui/src/Portal/Portal.js#L47)

